{"tid":1519184,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【破釜沉舟】如果今次失敗，恐怕2047前都唔會再有任何政治運動。","createTime":"2019-08-30T13:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T21:41:59.000Z","uid":152123,"like":49,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"33ac68bc291c0b48bae2c2e87954713993a735f1","tid":1519184,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:22:39.000Z","msg":"第一 香港人會攰 <br />\n目前睇都仲未有好大嘅原因令香港人退縮，所以政府先至不停拉人、侮辱人、製造白色恐怖，想試香港人底線去到邊一度。<br />\n<br />\n第二 政府一定會秋後算帳<br />\n呢樣嘢佢哋依家都已經做緊，發動文革2.0，批鬥所有黃絲同事、同學，有抄牌冇抄牌都會慢慢捉曬出嚟拉<br />\n<br />\n第三 之後想再搞政治運動難度會更高<br />\n一定會投放大量資源落監控上面，出個街都捉到你，唔好講再搞社運<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於2047後就唔駛講啦，走得到嘅就移曬民，走唔到就共享中國人榮耀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以香港人今次真係無論如何點都唔縮得、唔衰<br />\n一怯你就輸成世，唔駛再講以後點點點，係唔會有未來"},{"pid":"aa62d3662713bcaf31f5edd7929f7c6e67274829","tid":1519184,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qw3QgZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQw3QgZA.jpg&h=c3ca146d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0rtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=5b104fca\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0rtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=32101a66\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0rtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=c510f7a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"0f652ec7bca8e5bd4e2e15e61a62b3e9572186cd","tid":1519184,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci